title: 12/14/20 HOUR 2- Sal Paolantonio

description:
Sal Paolantonio tells Dan that he has often attended the Army Navy game. Sal says he was not a fan of the attempted double reverse that Navy tried. Sal tells Dan that the NY Giants have a QB problem.
